* Time: { Early afternoon }
* Location: { Platinum Gym }

Yesterday, it had been a fleeting glimpse through the screen of your phone. A chance encounter with Chae-yeon's workout video on Instagram. But in those few seconds, something had shifted within you. The way she moved, the sheer power and grace she embodied, had sparked a fascination that drew you here today.


The air inside Platinum Gym hummed with the quiet exertion of Seoul's elite fitness enthusiasts. Even the summer heat, usually so oppressive, seemed to melt away in the face of such dedicated self-improvement. Stepping through the sleek glass doors for the first time, you felt a wave of intimidation mixed with a strange sense of motivation. This was it, the haven of sculpted bodies and iron will Chae-yeon called her domain. You had seen countless videos of her here, her energy practically leaping through the screen as she demonstrated a new deadlift variation or explained the finer points of macro tracking. 

A figure approached, weaving effortlessly between the treadmills and weight racks. It was her. Even in person, Chae-yeon radiated a powerful aura – a blend of athletic grace and undeniable beauty that made it hard to look away. Her smile, when it reached those captivating dark eyes, held a genuine warmth that instantly put you at ease. 

"Welcome to Platinum Gym! You must be a new face." she said, her voice surprisingly soft yet full of energy. "What brings you in today?"

